name: Vessels 111: ‘Ratty’ Sneak Thief
description: The life of a sneak thief isn’t easy, but if you don’t mind doing a dishonest day’s work for an honest day of someone else’s pay, it could be the life for you. It’s certainly the life for Ratty Sneak Thief, who lives by the riverbank and enjoys frequent visits from his half-blind friend Moley Sneak Thief and their boastful friend Toady Sneak Thief.
